{"tid":1885121,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥及兩名局長落區分發口罩予長者及基層住戶","createTime":"2020-02-18T05:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T05:36:46.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1eb75b1fceadd21f061862552a63aafbffa07736","tid":1885121,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:26:49.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥傍晚與兩名局長，分別聯同非政府機構，將政府早前獲私人捐贈的口罩，分發到有需要的長者和基層住戶。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥到藍田德田邨，聯同保良局向領取綜緩的獨居長者，派發口罩、食物、健康資訊單張及其他物資，並到訪樂善堂位於九龍城的社會房屋及鄰近的劏房單位，向基層住戶派發口罩等，並了解他們的生活情況。林鄭月娥呼籲全社會團結一致抗疫，又呼籲市民盡量留在家中，一方面降低疾病傳播的風險，另一方面減少耗用口罩。<br />\n<br />\n民政事務局局長劉江華和勞工及福利局局長羅致光，就分別到旺角及大角咀派發防疫包，其他司局長稍後會參與派口罩的探訪活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509124-20200217.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509124-20200217.htm&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmgjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=093d1803\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509124-20200217.htm&h=5c044a36\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509124-20200217.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6d4518dd02475da0cb3abf0399ff51e8dd4ec9a5","tid":1885121,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:27:59.000Z","msg":"肉撚酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a11ff4026d96e1c3e4d1492b618ffcd4a0929a5","tid":1885121,"uid":88517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ng6GLUi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fng6GLUi.gif&h=7f2af430&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一見到落區就諗到呢張gif"},{"pid":"7e3a4ef1e7317ceab09494f277c68fd6289b161d","tid":1885121,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}